  characterSystem:
    characterName: Lawrence Douglaws
    hejFras: Hands up HAHA!
    hejFrasEvent:
      Guid:
        Data1: 929637637
        Data2: 1212304024
        Data3: -1395779149
        Data4: 1533497231
      Path: event:/Lawrence/Lawrence Hej
    firstQuestion:
      question: "Evening constable, hope I\u2019m not in trouble."
      answer: "Even if you were, there are way worse crooks around here. You\u2019ve
        heard the rumors right? Talk on the town is that this ball is one big cover
        up! I just know that scoundrel Mr. Allford has something to hide\u2026"
    q1FollowUpQuestion1:
      question: That sounds scary!
      answer: "I ain\u2019t no chicken! In this world you have to be brave to get
        what you want! So if you ain\u2019t got any moxie you can bugger off!"
    q1FollowUpQuestion2:
      question: I got to have some moxie talking to you, old timer.
      answer: HA! You got that right! I think I like the jib of your vibe, sport!
    secondQuestion:
      question: What does the constable like at a party?
      answer: "Good dancin\u2019 music! Can\u2019t stand when they play that classical
        nonsense. Bach? More like Barf, HA! Can\u2019t say I\u2019m a grandstand
        at the dancefloor though."
    q2FollowUpQuestion1:
      question: "I\u2019m sure you\u2019re not that bad!"
      answer: "Oh you weren\u2019t at the 1932 annual police gala. It still smells
        like pineapple under the floorboards HAHAHA!"
    q2FollowUpQuestion2:
      question: What happened at the 1932 police gala?
      answer: "My lawyer won\u2019 t like it if I speak any more on the matter\u2026
        the jist of it is, I ain\u2019t a good dancer!"
    thirdQuestion:
      question: Does it smell sweet in here or are you just sniffly?
      answer: "Ha! You\u2019re on the nose. I feel like I have a damned waterfall
        on my face!"
    q3FollowUpQuestion1:
      question: Do you need a tissue?
      answer: "I think \u2013 ACHOO! \u2013 there\u2019s a dog in here! I can't even
        stand the K9s at the station! "
    q3FollowUpQuestion2:
      question: Bless you.
      answer: "Thank you! Not only do I have to suffer allergy problems at my work,
        my cats hate it when I come home smelling like dog, they won't even let me
        come in. I wish there were no dogs HA! I\u2019m just pulling your leg\u2026
        kind of\u2026"
    "hejD\xE5Fras": "Don\u2019t cause any trouble out there. "
